summary: [SPOILERS] Anyone else think that every season of GoT is overall good?
title: [SPOILERS] Anyone else think that every season of GoT is overall good?
body:
Some are weaker than others and the last few probably have more flaws since they dont have source material anymore but I think even the weakest GoT season (for me its S5) is better than most tv shows and definitely still good.



Source: https://ift.tt/2QXS7Kx
